description: Returns a pre-signed URL that provides temporary download access to the specific email message stored in the archive.

parameters.name: ArchivedMessageId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the archived email message.

nested_items.name: From
nested_items.description: The RCPT FROM given by the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: Helo
nested_items.description: The HELO used by the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: To
nested_items.description: All SMTP TO entries given by the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: MessageDownloadLink
nested_items.description: A pre-signed URL to temporarily download the full message content.

nested_items.name: ConfigurationSet
nested_items.description: The name of the configuration set used when sent through a configuration set with archiving enabled.

nested_items.name: IngressPointId
nested_items.description: The ID of the ingress endpoint through which the email was received.

nested_items.name: RuleSetId
nested_items.description: The ID of the rule set that processed the email.

nested_items.name: SenderHostname
nested_items.description: The name of the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: SenderIpAddress
nested_items.description: The IP address of the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: SendingMethod
nested_items.description: The name of the API call used when sent through a configuration set with archiving enabled.

nested_items.name: SendingPool
nested_items.description: The name of the dedicated IP pool used when sent through a configuration set with archiving enabled.

nested_items.name: SourceArn
nested_items.description: Specifies the archived email source, identified by either a Rule Set's ARN with an Archive action, or a Configuration Set's Archive ARN.

nested_items.name: SourceIdentity
nested_items.description: The identity name used to authorize the sending action when sent through a configuration set with archiving enabled.

nested_items.name: Timestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the email was received.

nested_items.name: TlsCipherSuite
nested_items.description: The TLS cipher suite used to communicate with the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: TlsProtocol
nested_items.description: The TLS protocol used to communicate with the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: TrafficPolicyId
nested_items.description: The ID of the traffic policy that was in effect when the email was received.
